ATF Proposes Malibu Viti Area


     Responding to a petition from George Rosenthal, president,
Rancho Escondido Inc., the Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco and Firearms
proposed (60 Federal Register 66535) establishment of the
Malibu-Newton Canyon Viticultural Area in Los Angeles County.
     Comments due: Feb. 20 to Chief, Wine, Beer and Spirits
Regulations Branch, BATF, PO Box 50221, Washington, DC
20091-0221 (Attn: Notice No. 817).




