Buckles Named ATF Deputy Director


     Bradley A. Buckles was named deputy director of the Bureau
of Alcohol, Tobacco and Firearms, succeeding Daniel R. Black, who
retired Jan. 3.  Buckles was ATF's chief counsel prior to the promotion.




