LEISURE BEVERAGE INSIDER via NewsNet
JANUARY 8, 1996

     Pepsi-Cola Co. has been awarded the 1995 Clear Choice Award

     Pepsi-Cola Co. has been awarded the 1995 Clear Choice Award
by the Glass Packaging Institute for its Smooth Moos Smoothies dairy
drink. The product's 9.5-oz. glass bottle, which is shaped like an
old-fashioned refillable milk bottle, won the award in the "new beverage
product" category.



