THE BEST ENTREPRENEURS

An amazing year for entrepreneurs! A new club was formed:
double-billionaire winners. Jim Clark did it once with Silicon Graphics and
came back with Netscape. Steve Jobs hit it big with Apple-took a long
break-and won again with Pixar. The hurdle was certainly raised in '95.

