THE BEST WEB SITES

THE SPOT(www.thespot.com)
A daily soap opera about twentysomethings.

EDGAR
(www.sec.gov/edgarhp.htm)
Repository for sec filings by companies since '94.

CENSUS
(www.census.gov)
If it's demographic information you want, this is the place.

