FORD FOUNDATION PROGRAM BUDGETS, 1988-1991

(fiscal years October 1-September 30, in millions of dollars)
---------------------------------------------------------
                                      1988-89   1990-91
Major Program Areas:
     Urban Poverty                      82.7      87.2
     Rural Poverty and Resources        59.7      56.9
     Human Rights and Social Justice    58.7      63.0
     Governance and Public Policy       46.5      54.5
     Education and Culture              73.5      79.4
     International Affairs              41.9      43.3
Other Program Allocations*              46.2      61.5
Program Related Investments             25.0      30.7
Program Support                         45.8      53.2
General Reserve                         50.0      70.0
                                        -----     -----
Totals                                  530.0     599.7

* Includes allocations for population activities, special program
activities, and unanticipated needs within each program area.
Source: "Current Interests of the Ford Foundation," Ford
Foundation, Office of Communications.



