NEW HOTLINE PROVIDES FUEL PRICE DATA

Find up-to-date information on gasoline and diesel fuel prices by 
calling a new FREE National Energy Information Center hotline at 202-
586-6966.  The data were formerly provided by the now defunct 
Interstate Commerce Commission.



