GUIDE TO DEFENSE-RELATED INFORMATION

HOW TO GET IT:  A GUIDE TO DEFENSE-RELATED INFORMATION RESOURCES 
describes Defense-related information available through publications; 
organizations; programs and services; and software, data bases, and 
automated information services.
 
The GUIDE, Order No. AD-A298436, costs $11 from the Reference Services 
Division, Defense Technical Information Center, 8725 John J. Kingman 
Road, Suite 0944, Fort Belvoir, VA  22060-6218, 800-225-3842; fax 703-
767-9070; e-mail "msorders@dtic.mil".  The reference is also available 
on diskette in Word for Windows or Mac-compatible Word versions for 
$20.  For PCs, cite Order No. AD-M000517; for Macintosh, cite Order No. 
AD-M000518.



